  "time_ut": 1661065006,
  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u2019\u0db6\u0dd2\u0dad\u0dca\u0dad\u0dbb \u0d9c\u0dd0\u0dc3\u0da7\u0dca\u0da7\u0dd4\u0dc0\u2019 \u0dbb\u0dd2\u0dc0\u0dc3\u0dca \u0d9a\u0dd2\u0dbb\u0dd3\u0db8\u0d9a\u0dca \u0db1\u0dd1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "There is no reversal of the 'egg gazette'",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "\"The consumer authority has gazetted a control price of Rs. 45/= for eggs. This was done to protect both the poultry producer and the consumer. Legal action will definitely be taken if any action is taken to sell eggs at a price higher than the control price.\" Consumer and Food Safety Minister Naleen Fernando said while calling a press conference in Ja-Ala.",
        "\"During the last two or three weeks, the consumers had to pay a lot of money for eggs. People went on social media saying not to eat eggs. When there was a public opinion that they should not eat eggs, I instructed the Consumer Authority to investigate this. The experts on the prices of the Consumer Authority This step was taken after looking at various aspects.",
        "This will not cause injustice to the producer or the consumer. We set a control price of Rs. 45/= for eggs that were priced at Rs. 20/= to Rs. 25/=. In the past, the price of an egg went from 60 to 65 rupees. The price has been fixed after calculating all the costs of the producer and even the interest on the money borrowed.",
        "Some egg producers say that they have increased the price to compensate for the recent loss. It is a normal situation. There is no way to make profit for the past except to act accordingly after those businesses return to normal.",
        "If eggs have to be imported, it depends on the behavior of the egg producer. However, the Consumer Authority is an independent body. Those who sell eggs for more than Rs 45/= know how they work. Only if you don't act like that, I will have to see. If we make a decision, we will work according to that decision. If the gazette is reversed, we should be reversed.\""
      ],
